&lt;h1 id="earnest"&gt;Earnest&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;December 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jessica and I have certain words that have special significance when we&amp;rsquo;re talking about startups. The highest compliment we can pay to founders is to describe them as &amp;ldquo;earnest.&amp;rdquo; This is not by itself a guarantee of success. You could be earnest but incapable. But when founders are both formidable (another of our words) and earnest, they&amp;rsquo;re as close to unstoppable as you get.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Pick Partners With Intelligence, Energy and Integrity</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/pick-partners-with-intelligence-energy-and-integrity/</link><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2019 12:58:19 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/pick-partners-with-intelligence-energy-and-integrity/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/naval/zh/pick-partners-with-intelligence-energy-and-integrity.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
