&lt;h1 id="pick-partners-with-intelligence-energy-and-integrity"&gt;Pick Partners With Intelligence, Energy and Integrity&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mar 22 2019&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can&amp;rsquo;t compromise on any of these three&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
