&lt;h1 id="make-luck-your-destiny"&gt;Make Luck Your Destiny&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mar 7 2019&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Build your character in a way that luck becomes deterministic&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nivi:&lt;/strong&gt;
I think it&amp;rsquo;s pretty interesting that the first three kinds of luck that you described there are very common cliches for them that everybody knows. And then for that last kind of luck that comes to you out of the unique way that you act, there&amp;rsquo;s no real cliche for it.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Mean</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_en/mean/</link><pubDate>Sat, 01 Nov 2014 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_en/mean/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_zh/mean/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
